    <description>Reserved by IETF</description>
    <xref type="rfc" data="rfc3513"/><xref type="rfc" data="rfc4291"/>
    <notes>This range has been partially allocated. See <xref type="registry" data="iana-ipv6-special-registry"/> for details. ::/96, formerly defined as the "IPv4-compatible IPv6 address" prefix, was deprecated by <xref type="rfc" data="rfc4291"/>.</notes>
